Alibaba Group Holding | Asia Pacific
BABA 1QF26: CMR line, cloud beat, e-com profit in line
Unchanged Impact to our thesis
In- line Financial results versus consensus
Largely unchanged Direction of next 12- month consensus EPS
Source: Company data, Morgan Stanley Research

Total revenues \(+2\%\) YoY, in line \((+10\%\) exe Sun Art and Intime); CMR \(+10\%\) in line. Quick commerce \(+12\%\) Taobao monthly active consumers \(+25\%\) YoY in Aug. Cloud \(+26\%\) YoY, beat MSe by \(3\%\) . Al- related triple digit for 8 quarters. Adjusted EBITA \(-14\%\) YoY, beat MSe by \(3\%\) . E- com group (TTG + quick commerce) adjusted EBITA \(-21\%\) YoY, largely in line with MSe. 1Q Capex accelerated QoQ to Rmb 38.7bn vs Rmb24.6bn in 4Q. Repurchased 7mn ADS for US0.8bn vs 51mn ADSs for US\$0.6bn.
